 .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":105,"searchDepth":118,"depth":118,"links":505},[506,507,508],{"id":14,"depth":118,"text":15},{"id":22,"depth":118,"text":23},{"id":43,"depth":118,"text":44},"2019-06-20 10:52:16","A project might need me to write CoffeeScript, so I figured I'd poke at it a bit and figure out what this thing actually is. CoffeeScript isn't a brand-new language — it's a transpiled language that compiles down to JavaScript. This post walks through setting it up with Gulp and the basic syntax: variables, functions, objects, arrays, conditionals, and loops.","md","en",{},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002Fcoffeescript-basics","3",{"title":6,"description":510},false,"en\u002FJavaScript\u002Fcoffeescript-basics",[61,520],"CoffeeScript",null,"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F20\u002Fcoffeescript-basics\u002F","vphmYadIsvQ3eGPHL0f7Bv5d5qrtsAJRvboVVcmrhHo",{"newer":525,"older":529},{"url":526,"title":527,"date":528},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F21\u002Fcoffeescript-event-not-firing\u002F","CoffeeScript Event Not Firing? It Was the Parentheses All Along","2019-06-21 10:19:54",{"url":530,"title":531,"date":532},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F19\u002Fjavascript-flatten-multidimensional-arrays\u002F","5 Ways to Flatten a Multidimensional Array in JavaScript (Including the ES2019 One)","2019-06-19 14:45:37",[534,539,544],{"url":535,"title":536,"date":537,"readingMinutes":538},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2026\u002F03\u002F10\u002Fweb-crypto-api-encryption-guide\u002F","No crypto Package, No Node.js — The Web Crypto API Does It All in the Browser","2026-03-10 09:45:08","9",{"url":540,"title":541,"date":542,"readingMinutes":543},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2025\u002F12\u002F08\u002Fjquery-why-it-declined\u002F","jQuery Was Once King — So Why Did It Fall Off?","2025-12-08 21:35:24","7",{"url":545,"title":546,"date":547,"readingMinutes":548},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2025\u002F12\u002F05\u002Fjavascript-generator-functions\u002F","What Are JavaScript Generator Functions (function*)? The Function You Can Pause and Resume","2025-12-05 13:40:31","5",1784012774618]